title: Finland's leaders announce support for NATO membership, moving nation closer to joining alliance
content:
1. Finland's leaders announce support for NATO membership, moving nation closer to joining alliance  CNN
  2. Finland president, prime minister, urge the country to apply for NATO membership 'without delay'  Fox News
  3. Watch again: Boris Johnson and Finnish President give update after Ukraine meeting  The Independent
  4. Biden and NATO finally confront Putin — but must do more to stop him  The Hill
  5. Finland Says It Will Apply to Join NATO in Response to Russia's Ukraine Invasion  The Wall Street Journal
